column5: Mexican-American-Cambodian athlete ------Jessa Khan------ won another gold medal for Cambodia after defeating her opponent from the Philippines in the 49 kg jujitsu category. The match was won by Jessa on technical points after a 2-2 draw.------This is Cambodia’s ------fourth ------gold ------medal------
column6: which has put Cambodia seventh in the table with a total of 36 medals- four gold
